to hijack the shipment

52:20.291 --> 52:22.000
and no one
shows up,

52:22.083 --> 52:24.333
he'll figure
someone talked.

52:25.375 --> 52:28.083
Dillon:
Look, I know you're not
big on taking my advice,

52:28.166 --> 52:30.875
but you better make sure
he doesn't think it's you.

52:30.959 --> 52:32.417
Jett:
Soon as I get
back, I will.

52:32.500 --> 52:33.792
Where are you going?

52:33.875 --> 52:36.542
Uh, spa weekend
with a girlfriend.

52:37.709 --> 52:39.375
Somehow, I can't
picture that.

52:40.667 --> 52:42.875
Some people lack vision.

52:52.709 --> 52:55.792
♪ ♪

53:20.041 --> 53:21.750
Good morning,
Rosalie.

53:23.625 --> 53:25.417
I have to go to work now and...

53:25.500 --> 53:28.792
didn't know if you preferred
coffee or tea first thing.

53:30.709 --> 53:31.917
What's wrong?

53:32.041 --> 53:33.458
Turn around.

53:34.500 --> 53:36.083
What are you doing?

53:36.166 --> 53:38.166
I said turn around.

53:38.250 --> 53:39.333
Slow.

53:44.959 --> 53:46.583
What did we say
about self-control--

53:46.667 --> 53:49.291
(tray clatters)

53:53.792 --> 53:56.959
♪ ♪

54:23.333 --> 54:26.458
♪ ♪

54:53.333 --> 54:56.500
♪ ♪

55:42.917 --> 55:45.417
♪ ("JETT" THEME PLAYS) ♪

55:49.041 --> 55:50.750
-MAN: What's your name?
-(LOCK CLICKS)

55:51.000 --> 55:52.083
You know my name.

55:54.583 --> 55:56.000
-ALICE: (OVER PHONE) Mom?
-What's up, monkey?

55:56.083 --> 55:57.417
-ALICE: Where are you?
-JETT: Just workin'.

55:57.750 --> 55:59.417
-Shh.
-(EXCLAIMS)

56:04.041 --> 56:06.417
MAN 2:
Nobody is coming to save you.

56:08.917 --> 56:11.041
-(CHUCKLING)
-(CHAINSAW BUZZES)

56:12.542 --> 56:15.083
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

56:16.917 --> 56:19.709
♪ (SMOOTH MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

56:19.792 --> 56:20.792
(ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)

56:23.542 --> 56:26.417
Episode five starts a little bit
with a timeout.

56:27.083 --> 56:30.458
Charlie and Jett are having
their next date

56:30.750 --> 56:33.125
that he wondered if she would
actually want to have.

56:33.208 --> 56:34.333
SEBASTIAN GUTIERREZ:
We get a really good sense

56:34.625 --> 56:37.625
as to how much she and Charlie
like each other as people.

56:37.709 --> 56:40.625
If Jett gets nervous at all,
she's a little nervous here.

56:40.709 --> 56:42.959
And these coincidences
that are piling up,

56:43.375 --> 56:45.458
it's not gonna take very long
for Charlie

56:45.542 --> 56:47.625
to start putting together
that Jett might be involved.

56:47.709 --> 56:49.542
You gonna tell me how you really
got hurt?

56:49.625 --> 56:50.709
CARLA GUGINO:
She makes up this story

56:50.792 --> 56:52.417
about waking up
and sleepwalking.

56:52.500 --> 56:53.709
If I did,
you'd never believe it.

56:53.792 --> 56:55.375
You know, she knows
that he knows her pretty well.

56:55.458 --> 56:58.000
I think if anyone could see
a tell, it would be him.

56:58.083 --> 56:58.917
Try me.

56:59.000 --> 57:00.709
We realize that part of this
is true.

57:00.792 --> 57:03.000
Like, she is actually revealing
things about herself

57:03.083 --> 57:04.291
that she normally wouldn't,

57:04.375 --> 57:07.083
and so this is mixing
truth and fiction.

57:07.166 --> 57:09.083
Different characters here are
technically betraying

57:09.166 --> 57:11.375
the other characters, so Jett
is collecting information

57:11.458 --> 57:12.417
that will hurt Charlie.

57:12.500 --> 57:14.083
JETT: What are you gonna do
about Salas?

57:14.166 --> 57:16.709
Ah, he's got a boat full of
heroin docking here next week.

57:16.792 --> 57:18.959
GUTIERREZ: This is a world
where life really is cheap.

57:19.041 --> 57:21.458
And the only person
he can say that to is Jett.

57:21.542 --> 57:23.125
And of course,
Jett is one person

57:23.208 --> 57:26.750
who's actually working
with the cops to bring him down.

57:26.834 --> 57:28.542
Ah, it's a mess of a setup.

57:28.875 --> 57:30.291
There's only one exit route.

57:31.875 --> 57:32.750
What would you do?

57:32.959 --> 57:34.625
And also, she does have
a soft spot for him,

57:34.709 --> 57:35.709
there's no doubt about it.

57:36.000 --> 57:36.792
Given a choice,

57:37.166 --> 57:39.000
I never go in somewhere
with only one exit route.

57:39.834 --> 57:40.667
(ROSALIE GASPS)

57:41.041 --> 57:43.792
This parallel story that
we've been seeing with Rosalie

57:43.875 --> 57:48.917
and Benny, who shot her lover,
has felt guilty the whole time.

57:49.000 --> 57:50.667
BENNY: It's what happens
when you lose control.

57:50.750 --> 57:53.041
It happens sometimes.
you just have to learn from it.

57:53.542 --> 57:54.375
(SIGHS)

57:54.709 --> 57:56.458
There's no shame in fate,
Rosalie.

57:56.917 --> 57:59.333
Not in a perfect world,
not at the scene of the crime.

58:00.125 --> 58:00.875
(THUD)

58:01.375 --> 58:04.291
And that story... (CHUCKLES)
is gonna take other turns.

58:04.792 --> 58:06.375
What did we say
about self-control?
